Coronation Street funeral and return: 10 spoilers you need to know next week


It’s a week of hellos and goodbyes in Coronation Street next week – with many residents lamenting the loss of the ones they have lost and others welcoming home a much missed friend and partner. 


While Carla and Cathy are delighted by the return of Roy to Weatherfield, Jason says farewell to his departed dad, Tony, Nick prepares to end his relationship, Jenny remembers one of her darkest moments of loss – and Craig experiences his first broken heart.

We have pulled together all of the information you need to know to prepare yourself for another dramatic week on the cobbles.



Here are your spoilers from the week commencing Monday 9th May


